Class LoShuMagicSquare

  • java.lang.Object
    • LoShuMagicSquare
  • class LoShuMagicSquare
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides the variables, constructor, and methods to generate a square with the values 1 through 9 and determine if it is a Lo Shu Magic Square.
    Since:
    2021-04-10
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Alexander Laudino

      private int[][] square
